    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Customer Reply Assistant\\n\",\"**NLP Project 55 of 100** — Generate support responses in brand tone from customer queries.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import requests, pandas as pd\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"tickets = [\\n    {'query':'My order has not arrived after 2 weeks.','category':'Shipping'},\\n    {'query':'I was charged twice for my subscription.','category':'Billing'},\\n    {'query':'The app keeps crashing on my phone.','category':'Technical'},\\n    {'query':'How do I upgrade to the premium plan?','category':'Sales'},\\n]\\n\\nBRAND_TONE = 'friendly, empathetic, professional'\\n\\ndef generate_reply(ticket, model='qwen3:1.7b'):\\n    prompt = f\\\"\\\"\\\"Generate a customer support reply for this query. Tone: {BRAND_TONE}. Keep under 60 words.\\nCategory: {ticket['category']}\\nQuery: {ticket['query']} /no_think\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n    try:\\n        r = requests.post('http://localhost:11434/api/generate',json={'model':model,'prompt':prompt,'stream':False},timeout=60)\\n        return r.json().get('response','')\\n    except:\\n        replies = {'Shipping':'We\\\\'re sorry about the delay! Let me track your order right away. Can you share your order number?',\\n                   'Billing':'I apologize for the billing issue. I\\\\'ll look into this immediately and ensure you get a refund for the duplicate charge.',\\n                   'Technical':'Sorry to hear about the crashes! Please update to the latest version. If it persists, we\\\\'ll escalate to our engineering team.',\\n                   'Sales':'Great to hear you\\\\'re interested in Premium! You can upgrade from Settings > Subscription, or I can help you right here.'}\\n        return replies.get(ticket['category'], 'Thank you for reaching out. Let me look into this for you.')\\n\\nfor t in tickets:\\n    reply = generate_reply(t)\\n    print(f'Customer: {t[\\\"query\\\"]}')\\n    print(f'Reply: {reply}\\\\n')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Brand tone consistency** is maintained through prompt engineering.\\n\",\"- **Category-specific templates** ensure relevant responses.\\n\",\"- **LLMs add personalization** and natural language quality.\\n\",\"- **For production, integrate with helpdesk tools** (Zendesk, Intercom).\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
